---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="¡Suscripción Confirmada! — Ingeniería sin filtros" 
  description="Gracias por confirmar tu suscripción. Acá tenés tu Blueprint de Arquitectura."
  navVariant="blog"
  footerVariant="simple"
>
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Brand elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -mr-48 -mt-48"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -ml-48 -mb-48"></div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl w-full text-center relative z-10 space-y-10">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent text-sm font-mono tracking-widest uppercase animate-pulse">
          Acceso Concedido
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-txt-primary tracking-tight">
          ¡Bienvenido a bordo, <span class="text-accent">Senior.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-txt-secondary max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Ya sos parte de la comunidad de Ingeniería sin filtros. <br/>
          Como prometido, acá tenés tu material de alto valor.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PDF Download Card -->
      <div class="p-1 md:p-1.5 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/20 to-transparent border border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="bg-bg-surface rounded-[22px] p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 text-left">
          <!-- Mockup Mini -->
          <div class="relative w-40 h-56 shrink-0 bg-[#0a0f1a] rounded-lg shadow-xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden rotate-[-3deg] hidden sm:block">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div class="text-[6px] font-mono text-accent opacity-50">>_ ISF</div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-lg font-bold leading-none text-white">ARCH</div>
                <div class="text-xl font-black leading-none text-accent">RED FLAGS</div>
              </div>
              <div class="h-1 w-full bg-accent/20"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-txt-primary">Architecture Red Flags</h2>
              <p class="text-txt-secondary font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-tighter">& The Modern Backend Blueprint (PDF)</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a 
                href="/assets/architecture-red-flags.pdf" 
                download
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-accent text-bg-deep font-bold hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(52,211,153,0.3)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="15" y2="3"/></svg>
                Descargar PDF Ahora
              </a>
              <a 
                href="/blog" 
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-bg-deep border border-border-subtle text-txt-primary font-bold hover:bg-bg-surface transition-all"
              >
                Ir al Blog
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-10 border-t border-border-subtle/50">
        <p class="text-sm text-txt-muted max-w-md mx-auto italic">
          "La diferencia entre un Senior y un Arquitecto es la capacidad de ver el desastre antes de que ocurra. Este PDF es tu primer paso."
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-txt-muted font-mono tracking-tighter pt-4">
        >_ INGENIERÍA SIN FILTROS · ALAFOURCA.DEV
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
